Author: Shootmeffs
Text: [TW numbers] I'm a fool, I played myself. I found more wine and am gonna get blackout drunk (probably). I also had at least 900 calories of food alone so I fucking hate myself. I don't have a scale (thank God) but if I look bigger tomorrow I will fucking scream. 900 is so much I'm actually crying and that is only food. I had so much alcohol it's probably twice as much as my food intake soooo... If I don't stay sober tomorrow imma off myself :) (I won't but ffs why can't I just stay fucking sober)
